OL,3,CFormer minister raises new concerns
OL,4,Cover state pension errors
OL,6,FFresh evidence that errors are still
OL,7,Fbeing made with some state pension
OL,8,Fclaims has been uncovered, according
OL,9,Fto a former pensions minister.
OL,11,FThe Department for Work and Pensions
OL,12,F(DWP) has been undertaking a
OL,13,Fcorrection exercise since 2021 to fix
OL,14,Fprevious state pension errors relating
OL,15,Fto certain groups of people, including
OL,16,Fsome widows and widowers.
