OL,3,CFormer minister raises new concerns
OL,4,Cover state pension errors
OL,6,FBut Sir Steve Webb, a former pensions
OL,7,Fminister who is now a partner at LCP
OL,8,F(Lane Clark & Peacock) said he had
OL,9,Ffound evidence of a new group of cases
OL,10,Fwhere incorrect information was given.
OL,12,FIt involves people claiming the new
OL,13,Fstate pension who were already widowed
OL,14,Fwhen they retired.
