OL,3,CFormer minister raises new concerns
OL,4,Cover state pension errors
OL,6,FSir Steve said he had been contacted
OL,7,Fby four separate people who had not
OL,8,Fbeen awarded any inherited state
OL,9,Fpension when they retired and had been
OL,10,Ftold in writing or over the phone by
OL,11,Fthe department that they were not
OL,12,Fentitled.
OL,14,FIn all four cases, this was incorrect
OL,15,Fand an increased amount of state
OL,16,Fpension has been arranged and arrears
OL,17,Fhave been paid, Sir Steve said.
