OL,3,CFormer minister raises new concerns
OL,4,Cover state pension errors
OL,6,FIn two of the cases, the underpayment
OL,7,Famounted over #2,000 per year, which
OL,8,Fcould potentially add up to a #40,000
OL,9,Fshortfall over a typical retirement.
OL,11,FSir Steve said one of the people he
OL,12,Fdealt with had said: "I personally
OL,13,Fwould like to see more people come
OL,14,Fforward to claim what is rightfully
OL,15,Ftheirs."
