OL,6,FIn general, the new group appears to
OL,7,Finclude those who are widows or
OL,8,Fwidowers at the point when they claim
OL,9,Ftheir new state pension and where
OL,10,Feither the spouse who has died reached
OL,11,Fpension age before April 6 2016 or
OL,12,Fwhere they died before April 6 2016,
OL,13,FSir Steve said.
