OL,3,CFormer minister raises new concerns
OL,4,Cover state pension errors
OL,6,FThe exact amount of inherited state
OL,7,Fpension depends on individual
OL,8,Fcircumstances, but could be higher if
OL,9,Fthe late spouse was an employee,
OL,10,Frather than self-employed and the
OL,11,Fwidowed spouse is not receiving a
OL,12,Fwidow's pension from a company pension
OL,13,Fscheme (as this may replace part of
OL,14,Fany inherited state pension due).
OL,16,FSir Steve said: "Having had to spend
OL,17,Fyears checking hundreds of thousands
OL,18,Fof historic state pension calculations
OL,19,Ffor errors, you would hope that DWP
OL,20,Fwould be making sure that new claims
OL,21,Fare handled correctly.
