OL,6,F"But we have found worrying evidence
OL,7,Fthat this is not the case.
OL,9,F"There seems to be a particular
OL,10,Fproblem for people who are widows or
OL,11,Fwidowers when they claim their state
OL,12,Fpension.
OL,14,F"In some cases DWP seems to have
OL,15,Ffailed to automatically add any
OL,16,Finherited state pension they were due
OL,17,Ffrom a late partner.
OL,19,F"These cases may well be the tip of an
OL,20,Ficeberg."
