OL,6,FA DWP spokesperson said: "We want to
OL,7,Fensure pensioners receive all the
OL,8,Fsupport to which they are entitled and
OL,9,Fhave a tool to help them understand
OL,10,Fwhat state pension they can inherit.
OL,12,F"Delays can occur to a customer's
OL,13,Fstate pension award when not all the
OL,14,Finformation we need is provided.
OL,16,F"In these cases, we will make a state
OL,17,Fpension award based on the customer's
OL,18,Fown national insurance record until we
OL,19,Fhave the required information.
